          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-1605095961302-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the<strong> chopped pepper</strong>, <strong>courgette</strong> <strong>chunks</strong> and<strong> onion wedges</strong> to a baking tray with a generous drizzle of <strong>olive oil </strong>and a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and <strong>pepper</strong></p><p>Tip: Cooking for 4 or more? Use 2 trays!</p><p>Put the tray[s] on the bottom shelf of the oven and cook for 30 min or until golden and cooked through – this is your <strong>roasted veg</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-1605095971492-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-1605095971492-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
