            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Stir through your <strong>tortiglioni</strong>,<strong> </strong>then cover with a lid and put the dish in the oven for 25-30 min or until the pasta is cooked through</p><p>Tip: Nestle as much of the pasta as you can into the sauce to help it cook evenly!</p><p>Give the <strong>tortiglioni</strong> a stir and the <strong>roasted veg</strong> on the tray a good mix up after 15 min</p><p>Use this time to clear up, set the table, have a cup of tea or simply chill!</p>",
