    {
      "instruction": "<p>To serve, stir the<strong> roasted veg </strong>through the pasta and season with a generous pinch of <strong>salt </strong>– this is your <strong>baked ratatouille tortiglioni</strong></p><p>Crumble your<strong> goats' cheese</strong> all over</p><p>Season with a grind of <strong>black pepper</strong></p><p>Dig in!</p>",
